g src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63519f414e9a0324d92fd77ddbe35582ab8c5797","tid":1540760,"uid":9694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:34:11.000Z","msg":"做橡皮圖章之嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主題錯左<br />\n應該係評對支共管理評分"},{"pid":"80149c22ffe678faf68397bc98e03760edb6c2bd","tid":1540760,"uid":107138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LgdcLSU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLgdcLSU.jpg&h=7d8fce73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ktasvY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ktasvY.jpg&h=e8e5ebbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WwTmzaZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwTmzaZ.jpg&h=1a577aad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a889SFe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa889SFe.jpg&h=3fb438bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機場壓力測試，其實係連「機場」都唔需要入的<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531743\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531743</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3fe0babd057a311eccd725131f83c86ee29c0388","tid":1540760,"uid":233982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:35:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gZAoYN3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i